  "text": "The energies that were excreted in the feces and urine were subtracted from the intake of GE to calculate the DE and ME for each diet [CITATION_1] . The DE and ME in the diet were then divided by 0.967 to calculate the DE and ME in corn. Nitrogen data were calculated as described by [CITATION_2] .",
